dc_title_s: Pre-Development Natural Resource Inventory by Land Tract: Prince George's County, Maryland
dc_description_s: Natural Resource Inventories depict the existing features found on a tract of land prior to subdivision. They include all existing site features, historic features, and the regulated natural resources necessary to evaluate a site prior to development. Natural Resource Inventories are reviewed by the M-NCPPC EPS staff for signature approval. A signed NRI must accompany a preliminary plan application.
